  * [36edd3c] git-dch: Support --nmu, --bpo and --qa. (Closes: #561535)
  * [7200035] git-dch: Pass dch_options to all calls of spawn_dch. This fixes
    the problem of an empty [maintainer] at the end of the changelog section.
